┌─────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│ Lasan JS - The Framework for Web Interfaces │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────┘

⦿ Performance is the key.
⦿ Security is the foundation.
⦿ Fully open-source.

□ Features

There are lots of features in Lasan JS, some of them are:
  ⬦ Seamless CSS/SCSS and JavaScript/TypeScript support.
  ⬦ File and Memory based rendering.
  ⬦ Custom templating language.
  ⬦ Reactive data binding.
  ⬦ And many more...

Read the full documentation to know more about Lasan JS.

□ Packages

Lasan JS is organized as a monorepo, comprising several integrated packages that together
form a comprehensive web framework. Below is the list of packages:
  ⬦ @lasan.js/template: Template engine for HTML, CSS, and JS (See packages/template)

□ Documentation

The official documentation for Lasan JS is available at docs/ directory.

